If you target anyone with verbal, online or physical abuse because of their race, religion, sexual orientation, disability or transgender identity – you may be committing a hate crime.

Find out more, including how to report a hate crime, on our website: https://t.co/htpxVrpTHA https://t.co/06RQ1gYzgJ
